Citation.sTitle: Solubility in binary solvent mixtures: pyrene dissolved in alcohol + toluene mixtures
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of pyrene in mixed solvents (methanol+toluene, ethanol+toluene and 2-propanol+toluene) were determined at temperatures between 283 K and 333 K by a gravimetric method. The experimental data were correlated with the Apelblat model. The calculated values of Apelblat model were found to show a fine representation of the experimental data
